name: BARTENDER VR SIMULATOR
summary: Bartender VR Simulator featuring five unique bars, popular cocktail recipes, and renowned bartending techniques, it’s one of the most immersive VR games, crafted with six-time World Bartending Champion, Tomek Malek.   Now with mixed reality and hand tracking, mix drinks using just your hands, no controllers needed! Get ready to shake, stir, and serve like never before.
